    "content": "## What Are Progressive Web Apps?\n\nProgressive Web Apps combine the best features of websites and mobile applications. They load like regular websites but offer app-like capabilities such as offline functionality, push notifications, and home screen installation. For UK businesses, PWAs solve the challenge of delivering a high-quality mobile experience without the development and distribution costs of native apps.\n\n## Benefits for the UK Market\n\nPWAs load quickly even on slow networks, which is crucial in areas of London with unreliable internet connectivity. They require significantly less storage space than native apps, making them accessible on budget smartphones. Push notifications re-engage users effectively. Users can add your PWA to their home screen without visiting an app store, reducing friction in the user journey. Major UK brands like Amazon UK and Argos have already adopted PWAs with impressive results.",
    "category": "Web Development",
    "author": "Boyzeth Solutions Team",
