    "slug": "retargeting-strategies-nigerian-ecommerce",
    "title": "Retargeting Strategies for UK E-Commerce Businesses",
    "excerpt": "Win back abandoned carts and lost visitors with retargeting campaigns designed for UK shoppers.",
    "content": "## The Retargeting Opportunity\n\nCart abandonment is a major challenge for e-commerce businesses worldwide, and the UK is no exception. Studies show that over 70% of online shopping carts are abandoned before purchase. Retargeting campaigns give you a second chance to convert these lost visitors by showing them relevant ads based on their browsing behavior.\n\n## Effective Retargeting Tactics\n\nSet up Facebook and Google retargeting pixels on your e-commerce site to track visitor behavior. Create segmented audiences based on specific actions — visitors who viewed products, added to cart but did not purchase, or completed a purchase. Serve personalized ads featuring the exact products they viewed, with compelling offers like free delivery in London or a limited-time discount. Use frequency capping to avoid overwhelming potential customers. Implement email retargeting for visitors who provided their email addresses but did not complete their purchase.",
