    "slug": "review-management-lagos-businesses",
    "title": "Review Management for UK Businesses: Building Trust Online",
    "excerpt": "Manage your online reviews effectively to build trust and attract more UK customers.",
    "content": "## The Power of Online Reviews\n\nIn London's interconnected business community, word-of-mouth has gone digital. Online reviews on Google, Facebook, and other platforms significantly influence purchasing decisions. A single negative review can cost you dozens of potential customers, while a collection of positive reviews builds credibility and drives business growth.\n\n## Best Practices for Review Management\n\nActively encourage satisfied customers to leave reviews on your Google Business Profile and other relevant platforms. Make the process easy by providing direct links. Respond to every review, positive or negative, within 24-48 hours. Thank reviewers for positive feedback and address negative reviews professionally, offering to resolve the issue offline. Never delete or hide negative reviews unless they violate platform policies. Use feedback from reviews to improve your products, services, and customer experience continuously.",
