    "title": "WhatsApp Marketing Strategies for UK Businesses",
    "excerpt": "Leverage the UK's most popular messaging app to drive sales and build customer relationships.",
    "content": "## WhatsApp's Dominance in the UK\n\nWhatsApp is by far the most popular messaging platform in the UK, with over 85% of smartphone users actively using the app. UK consumers prefer WhatsApp for business communication because it is familiar, convenient, and works well even on slow networks. This makes WhatsApp an essential channel for businesses of all sizes.\n\n## WhatsApp Business Features\n\nSet up WhatsApp Business with a complete profile including your business description, hours, address, and website. Use broadcast lists to send updates, offers, and announcements to interested customers. Automate responses with quick replies and away messages. Use labels to organize contacts and conversations. For larger operations, explore the WhatsApp Business API for integration with your CRM and customer support tools. Always obtain consent before adding customers to your broadcast lists and respect their communication preferences.",
