    "excerpt": "Analyze GBP insights data to make informed decisions and attract more local customers.",
    "content": "## What GBP Insights Tell You\n\nGoogle Business Profile provides valuable data about how customers find and interact with your listing. Insights show you how many people viewed your profile, how they found you (search vs. maps), what actions they took (website visits, direction requests, phone calls), and where they are located.\n\n## Making Data-Driven Decisions\n\nMonitor which search queries lead customers to your profile and optimize your content to target those terms. Identify peak times when customers are searching for your business and adjust your hours or staffing accordingly. Track direction requests to understand where your customers are coming from and consider location-specific marketing. Compare your insights with competitors to benchmark your performance. Use this data to inform your broader local SEO and marketing strategies, focusing on what drives the most valuable customer actions.",
