    "excerpt": "Implement effective digital marketing for your UK small business without breaking the bank.",
    "content": "## Marketing on a Budget\n\nSmall and medium enterprises in London often operate with tight marketing budgets, but limited funds do not have to mean limited results. A strategic approach that focuses on high-impact, low-cost channels can deliver impressive returns for SMEs willing to be creative and consistent.\n\n## Cost-Effective Digital Marketing Tactics\n\nFocus on organic search through SEO — it offers the best long-term ROI of any digital channel. Build an email list from day one and nurture leads with valuable content. Leverage social media organically by creating shareable content and engaging actively with your community. Use free tools like Google My Business, Canva for design, and social media scheduling tools. Repurpose content across multiple platforms to maximize reach without creating new content each time. Partner with micro-influencers who charge less but have highly engaged followings. Track everything and double down on what works.",
