    "excerpt": "More than half of all website traffic now comes from mobile devices. Find out why mobile optimisation is essential for SEO, user experience, and business growth.",
    "content": "## Why Mobile Optimisation Matters\n\nMore than half of all website traffic now comes from mobile devices. If your website isn't mobile-friendly, you could be losing customers every day.\n\n## What Is Mobile Optimisation?\n\nMobile optimisation means designing your website so it works smoothly on smartphones and tablets.\n\nThis includes:\n\n* Fast loading times\n* Responsive layouts\n* Easy-to-read text\n* Clickable buttons\n* Simple navigation\n\n## Why It's Important\n\n### Better User Experience\n\nVisitors stay longer when your site works well.\n\n### Higher Google Rankings\n\nGoogle uses mobile-first indexing.\n\n### More Conversions\n\nAn easy mobile experience leads to more enquiries and sales.\n\n### Lower Bounce Rates\n\nUsers leave quickly if your site is hard to use.\n\n## Common Mobile Issues\n\n* Text too small\n* Buttons too close together\n* Slow load speeds\n* Broken layouts\n\n## Final Thoughts\n\nMobile optimisation is no longer optional. It's essential for SEO, user experience, and business growth.",
