    "content": "## How to Rank Higher on Google\n\nRanking higher on Google helps your business get more visibility, traffic, and leads.\n\n## Key Ways to Improve Rankings\n\n### 1. Use the Right Keywords\n\nResearch what your audience is searching for.\n\n### 2. Create Quality Content\n\nAnswer questions and solve problems.\n\n### 3. Optimise Page Titles and Meta Descriptions\n\nThese help search engines understand your pages.\n\n### 4. Improve Website Speed\n\nGoogle rewards faster websites.\n\n### 5. Get Backlinks\n\nLinks from reputable websites improve authority.\n\n### 6. Mobile Optimisation\n\nYour website must work well on all devices.\n\n### 7. Local SEO\n\nOptimise your Google Business Profile and local keywords.\n\n## SEO Takes Time\n\nRanking higher doesn't happen overnight. Consistency is key.\n\nRegular updates, strong content, and technical optimisation can steadily improve your results.",
